Deirdre Kelly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deirdre_Kelly 0 Deirdre "Dee" Kelly (born 1971), also known as White Dee, is a British TV personality and actor. In 2014 and 2015 she appeared in the TV documentary series Benefits Street, and in 2014 she took part in Celebrity Big Brother. She plays "Liz" in the forthcoming film Ray Liz by Richard Billingham.In 2014 Kelly spoke at a Policy Exchange fringe meeting at the Conservative Party Conference in Birmingham.
